beer.beer_description:
Simcoe/Mosaic/Idaho-7

We may have been open for two years but we have been at 21 McCauley St for over three (cheers City of Sydney Council!). It's our little home so for our second birthday we have made a beer dedicated to our brewery/taproom and all the people who come to visit.

For our first birthday we released a little beer called Birthday Suit. It was our second DIPA and the first one we canned. You loved it, so DIPAs became a regular feature in our monthly releases.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 265 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 54!

items.checkin_comment: Tropical fruits, lime, melon and a lingering grassiness. Soft and creamy mouthfeel
